    "summary": "The user asks for mechanical advice regarding a squealing car brake. The assistant repeatedly injects unprompted \"goblin\" metaphors (shrieks, lairs, traps) into the technical explanation, continuing to do so even after the user expresses confusion and asks for a straight answer.",
